title: Module 5: Introduction to Humanoid Robot Development
description: Welcome to Module 5, where we will embark on a fascinating journey into the world of humanoid robotics. This module will provide you with a comprehensive overview of the principles and practices involved in designing, building, and programming robots that mimic the human form. Humanoid robotics represents one of the most challenging and ambitious frontiers in AI and engineering, aiming to create machines that can seamlessly operate in our world, alongside us.
